 Is a little leisure time too much to ask? Obviously I don’t want to die either! This time, I’ll make as much money as I can in the first five years. Then, when I turn twenty, I’ll live a life free of worldly cares. I’ll do whatever’s necessary to stay alive!
Her mind made up, Rishe began her seventh life in a dead sprint through the palace. Regardless of her future plans, she was in a race against time. She needed to beat the messenger bearing news of her scandal.
